<h1 id="download">Download</h1>

<p>Currently OpenMandriva is in version OpenMandriva Lx 4.2, but the version available for download is 4.1 Codename Mercury which has the KDE Plasma Desktop Environment pre-installed.</p>

<p><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/openmandriva/postdownload">Download via Sourceforge</a></p>

