<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<p>The installation of OpenMandriva is very intuitive and has a friendly graphical interface. To view all the steps, just click on this <a href="https://wiki.openmandriva.org/en/doc/guides/howto-install-steam">link</a> to get the step by step and all the necessary information.</p>

<h1 id="screenshots">Screenshots</h1>

<p>In addition to the post image of this post you can also get more screenshots to see how OpenMandriva is running before installing. To see the screenshots, use this <a href="https://gallery.openmandriva.org/index.php?/category/33">link</a>.</p>

